    dc:description "FIGURE 7. A: Dorsal view, B: ventral view, C: details of dorsal pholidosis, D: dorsal view of head, E: ventral view of head and F: lateral view of head of the holotype of Cyrtodactylus aaronbaueri sp. nov. (MZMU2015)" ;
